Description: Internet radio player for GNOME
 Receiver is a modern internet radio player for GNOME, featuring a curated
 collection of over 30,000 stations from around the world.
 .
 Features:
  * All stations pre-scanned and verified for reliability
  * Browse stations by genre, country, or search
  * Save your favourite stations for quick access
  * Beautiful native GNOME interface
  * Support for MP3, AAC, Ogg, and HLS streams
  * Session persistence - resume where you left off
